		<div class="c29content" data-content-id = "tcm:84-263335-16">
			<p  >In order to assist us in researching and resolving your concern, please provide the following information as available:</p> <p  >- Full Name (First, Middle, Last)</p> <p  >- Complete Address</p> <p  >- The full account number or other information to identify the account being disputed</p> <p  >- Last four digits of Social Security number</p> <p  >- Date of Birth</p> <p  >- Please describe the specific information that is inaccurate in the consumer report and the basis for the dispute</p> <p  >- Supporting documentation if available</p> <p  >- If the claim is related to identity theft, please provide documentation such as a police report or identity theft report if available</p>
